# All-Day Fitness — Commercial Gym Website

A modern, mobile-first website built for a commercial gym.  
Designed to showcase services, memberships, and facilities with a clean, professional UI and smooth interactions.

## Live Demo
https://erosrawr.github.io/gym-site/

## Features
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)
- Auto-sliding services carousel with images
- Membership tiers with clear feature breakdowns
- Bold “Why Choose Us” section
- Modern footer with social icons
- Clean navigation with mobile menu
- Smooth, non-intrusive animations

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox & Grid)
- Vanilla JavaScript

## Design Goals
- Commercial gym feel 
- Professional, confident tone
- Clean layout inspired by large fitness brands, while remaining original
- Optimized for readability and usability on mobile devices

## Status
Version 1 — complete and ready for customization or deployment.

